Package: kwtools-multi
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: kwtools-common (>= 0.8.3-3), cddb, cd-discid, cdparanoia, cdrdao (>=1.1.9), dvd+rw-tools, mjpegtools (>= 1.6.0), lame, genisoimage (>= 1.1.8), vcdimager
Suggests: kwtools-bin, ddrescue, vorbis-tools (>=1.0.0), wodim 
Description: Multimedia scripts
 Multimedia scripts to create VCD's, audio CD's, rip DVD's etc.
 .
 kwrecord: Burns audio, video, data CD's and ISO images, etc., onto CD-R(W) and
        DVD-+R(W).
 kwrip: Rips a complete CD into a certain directory. Video and audio.
 kwsnd2sndfm: Transforms different audio formats into different formats
        (raw,mp3,ogg,wav).
 kwvcdburn: Creates and burns video/photo CD's.
Homepage: http://www.netzworkk.de

